  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare the effect of Botox and casting to placebo and
      casting for reducing toe walking problems in children who are idiopathic toe walkers.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Patients who have been seen by one of the 5 paediatric orthopaedic surgeons at British
      Columbia's Children's Hospital and have been referred to the Shriner's gait lab for
      assessment of idiopathic toe walking will be eligible for the study.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
